This video shows you how to create five quick and easy large-format poster and photo applications using the HP Designjet Z5400 PostScript ePrinter. Learn how to print and finish:
- Simple poster hangers
- Presentation boards
- Photo frames
- Photo stands
- Photo wrap frame kits

Producing these products in-house can be an easy task with a high return. Copy shops often receive requests to print posters and photos, and they can be finished in many different ways. The HP Designjet Z5400 PostScript ePrinter is a great option for printing high-quality photo and large-format applications. Offering customers different finishes and techniques makes their prints special and can open up new revenue opportunities for your business.